SUMMARY:Family Painting Class: Poison Dart Frogs
DESCRIPTION:Learn about poison dart frogs while painting an up-close portrait of one of these amazing amphibians.  This class is perfect for all skill levels ages 5 & up. Your instructor will guide you through the process step-by-step while giving you the freedom to make it your own! \nEach painter will create and take home an 11″x14″ painting.  Participants are encouraged to wear comfortable clothing that may get messy. \nTickets are required for this event. \nBuy Tickets \n\nTicket Information:\n\nPrice: $40; $35 Members \nRecommended age: 5 & up \nEach ticket includes one canvas. All materials will be provided. \nMinors are required to be accompanied by an adult. Adults who are accompanying a minor and not painting are not required to purchase a ticket. \nRefund Policy: \n\n\nFull refund (minus a processing fee) if cancelled at least 1 week prior to class date.\n\n\n50% refund (plus tax) if cancelled at least 48 hours prior to class date.\n\n\nRefunds will not be issued for cancellations less than 48 hours prior to class date.\n\n\nTickets are not transferable to another class date.
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/family-painting-class-dart-frogs/
LOCATION:Downtown Raleigh\, 11 West Jones Street\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27601\, United States
CATEGORIES:All Ages,Classes,General Events,Natural World Investigate Lab,Special Events,Workshops
