SUMMARY:Nature PlaySpace Pop-Up (Whiteville)
DESCRIPTION:Come play outside with the Museum at Whiteville staff in our Nature PlaySpace\, a fenced-in outdoor play area at the Museum at Whiteville. Staff will guide children in an interactive activity aimed to get them outside and connected with nature. Make sure to dress for the weather! Pop-ups will take place in light rain or sunshine\, chilly or warm. In the event of more extreme weather\, call the Museum at Whiteville or check our social media pages for updates on the program’s status.  No registration required.  \nThis program is offered monthly on: \nFirst Saturdays \nThird Saturdays \n3:20 PM – 3:50 PM \nFor more information\, please call the Museum at Whiteville: 910-788-5100.
